{"tid":897121,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 一部iphone 變兩部！","createTime":"2018-11-10T15:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T16:14:14.000Z","uid":141800,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4af328d9a32ce508865c53e27ceb565ea26f4a","tid":897121,"uid":141800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n請問有冇巴打係蘋果做 可以嘅話唔該話我知個方法work 唔 work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假如你買咗AppleCare 你就會知道個規矩就係兩年內如果iPhone有任何損壞 可以以一個指定價格換取新iPhone<br />\n<br />\n假如我買咗一部新iPhone 然後將佢斬開兩件 首先以第一半以applecare 換取一部新iPhone <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相隔幾日後再以同樣理由換取一部新iPhone <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣會唔會順利成為首富？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5089cc77ef679d736a98c6d47e2a300b1f2519c4","tid":897121,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2573613ea5ca0d5f7331a87080fc6e8a45451f15","tid":897121,"uid":175645,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"Serial code 得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb46307679c9384336978a547fe4d08b38561da2","tid":897121,"uid":141800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2573613ea5ca0d5f7331a87080fc6e8a45451f15","tid":897121,"uid":175645,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"Serial